</li>
<li>
<p>$PackagingUnit — Contains an item’s packaging unit.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>$Position</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>$PreviewImage[1] …​$PreviewImage[25] — Returns the current item’s preview image.</p>
